sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Buyer
    participant Transfer as Transfer Orchestrator
    participant Queue as transfer_timeout_queue
    participant Consumer as Timeout Consumer
    participant TransferSvc as Transfer Service
    participant Market as Marketplace Service

    Buyer->>Transfer: initiate transfer
    Transfer->>Queue: publish timeout message with 24h TTL
    Note over Queue: wait until timeout expires
    Queue-->>Consumer: expired timeout message
    Consumer->>TransferSvc: GET current transfer state
    alt transfer still pending
        Consumer->>TransferSvc: PATCH status=cancelled
        Consumer->>Market: PATCH listing status=active
        Consumer-->>Transfer: cleanup complete
    else transfer already completed or cancelled
        Consumer-->>Queue: acknowledge and do nothing
    end
